    "asOf": "2023-11-08",
    "date": "2023-12-06T18:26:27Z",
    "text": "Payer State Transparency Act of 2023\n\nThis bill requires the Bureau of Economic Analysis of the Department of Commerce to calculate the federal tax burden of each state for each calendar year. It also requires the Office of Management and Budget to calculate the total amount of federal outlays received by each state in each fiscal year."
